    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Umber, that is a natural hydrated iron oxide with some oxide of manganese, that has not been heated and tends to a yellowish-brown color.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
